  "title": "MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description : </strong><br /></p><p>1. Develop strategic sales plans to achieve revenue, profit and market share targets<br />2. Analyze market trends and competitor activities to identify business opportunities<br />3. Monitor sales metrics and prepare performance reports for senior management<br />4. Oversee inventory management including demand forecasting and stock optimization<br />5. Ensure proper storage and rotation of perishable goods per food safety standards<br />6. Ensure compliance with local/state/federal food safety regulations (FDA, HACCP)<br />7. Implement and enforce hygiene/safety protocols in facilities and vehicles<br />8. Streamline processes to improve productivity and reduce operational costs<br />9. Utilize inventory management software and digital tools for operations10. Identify workflow bottlenecks and implement optimization solutions<br /></p><p></p><p><strong>Job Requirements: </strong><br /></p><p>1. 3-5 years management experience in food wholesale/distribution<br />2. Proven track record in sales targets, team management and inventory optimization<br />3. Experience with perishable food handling and storage management<br />4. In-depth knowledge of food safety regulations and wholesale operations<br />5. Proficiency in inventory management and CRM softwar<br />6. Strong analytical skills for data interpretation and decision-making<br />7. Excellent communication and negotiation abilities<br />8. Demonstrated leadership in team building and performance management<br />9. Be able to work on weekends and holidays, and be willing to work shifts</p>",
